{"tid":1590711,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"不如大家用Google Sheets整個制裁名單","createTime":"2019-09-24T00:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T00:18:35.000Z","uid":76710,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ece0aa2617b8d8c31edce3d80d7815573a670a9f","tid":1590711,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T00:48:57.000Z","msg":"有無手足整個檔案俾大家編輯<br />\n<br />\n持反普選 反人類 反民主等立場嘅<br />\n<br />\nD0級或以上官員/香港警察/公司董事/組織 佢本人及其直系親屬加入晒名單<br />\n<br />\n目的要佢地出唔到國 移民 做唔到生意<br />\n以國安為由 懇請政府移除佢地國籍<br />\n同埋令佢地子女讀唔到書 避唔到難<br />\n<br />\n西方政府其實好需要情報去做事<br />\n然後先可以令班人全面擁抱大灣區"},{"pid":"5e1a3f36eb6bc5d4942f8b0e2e8731bb7f3a5890","tid":1590711,"uid":7760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T00:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2145a02e3375418bc41c867ea26b97a2bde6da","tid":1590711,"uid":42920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:31:46.000Z","msg":"極重要推!!!!<br />\n我想講美國Solomon Yue已經講到明而家佢地需要一個制裁名單! 個名單係要有名、做左啲咩打壓民主既事同埋可靠證據! 我想問現時有無人係已經做緊依方面? 無既話應唔應該recruit個team專做依樣?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nVh21c3.png \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVh21c3.png%20&h=73e4f0c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c96822e98856dfbf234cb03d25acf3a8a012a21","tid":1590711,"uid":59211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dde7245b45254f2772c4eb600e7275f9efaa3e7","tid":1590711,"uid":59211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:05:40.000Z","msg":"【蒙面法要來了】<br />\n<br />\n成立《禁蒙面法推動組》記者會<br />\n<br />\n反修例風波持續，有暴徒自持蒙面，大肆破壞，對本港造成嚴重影響。為推動特區政府盡快訂立《禁蒙面法》，止暴制亂，我們將宣佈成立《禁蒙面法推動組》，一班來自政、商、法律、教育及退休公務員等的推動組成員將分享對《禁蒙面法》的看法及介紹未來工作計劃。<br />\n<br />\n日期：10月3日（星期四）<br />\n時間：下午3時<br />\n地點：南洋酒店宴會廰<br />\n出席：召集人及部份委員將出席記者會<br />\n<br />\n《禁蒙面法推動組》成員<br />\n顧問：<br />\n譚惠珠Maria Tam Wai-chu<br />\n譚耀宗TAM Yiu-chung<br />\n葉劉淑儀Regina Ip Lau Suk-yee<br />\n<br />\n召集人：<br />\n葛珮帆Elizabeth Quat<br />\n<br />\n委員：<br />\n張國鈞CHEUNG Kwok-kwan - 立法會議員<br />\n陳曼琪Chan Man Ki, Maggie - 律師, 港區人大代表<br />\n洪為民Witman HUNG - 港區人大代表<br />\n陳曉峰CHAN HIU FUNG, NICHOLAS - 律師, 港區人大代表<br />\n陳祖光 - 前警察員佐級協會主席, 退休警員<br />\n麥錦輝 MAK Kam-fai, Donny - 紀律部隊義工隊主席, 退休消防人員<br />\n胡明峰-國家行政學院香港同學會主席<br />\n孫名峯- 退休公務員<br />\n王吉顯WONG KIT HIN, PETER - 香港法律專業人員協會會長<br />\n楊全盛Eric Yeung - 香港青年聯會主席<br />\n冼漢迪Hendrick Sin  - 互聯網專業協會主席<br />\n屈穎妍 Chris Wat Wing-yin - 傳媒人<br />\n藍雪寶 - 老師<br />\n劉毅Ngai Victor Lau (Not Sure)- 律師<br />\n葉俊遠IP CHUN YUEN - 律師<br />\n黃河WONG HO, KEVIN - 律師"},{"pid":"5f37e6a8b467c397bcd90a9ebc7db8fa12135f38","tid":1590711,"uid":59211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:06:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%88%E5%AD%B8%E7%95%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0-%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E6%B3%95-%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E9%80%BE30%E4%BA%BA-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E7%9B%B4%E7%B3%BB%E8%A6%AA%E5%B1%AC%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%A7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%25E9%2580%25BE30%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E7%259B%25B4%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E5%258C%2585%25E6%258B%25AC%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%2585%25A7%2F&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obpMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=9a358df6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%259